  "title": "Assistant Project Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in preparing project documentation, including project plans, schedules, and reports.</li>\n  <li>Monitor project progress and identify potential delays or issues.</li>\n  <li>Serve as a point of contact for addressing inquiries and providing updates on project status.</li>\n  <li>Provide ad hoc support to the Project Team as needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/Diploma in management or a related field.</li>\n  <li>Proven experience in an administrative or assistant role, preferably in a project management environment.</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Preferably, fluent in Mandarin to effectively communicate with Mandarin-speaking clients.</li>\n</ul>",
